OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy morning with some patchy
OL,6,Flight rain. Increasingly bright spells
OL,7,Fdeveloping through the day and the odd
OL,8,Fshower possible. Then some rain in the
OL,9,Fwest in the late afternoon. Warm.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FRain will spread northeast
OL,12,Fthrough the evening, heavy for a time.
OL,13,FBecoming dry overnight with some clear
OL,14,Fspells but staying cloudy towards
OL,15,FArgyll and the Isles.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSaturday:FQuite cloudy to start but
OL,18,Fincreasingly bright or sunny weather
OL,19,Fdeveloping through the morning.
OL,20,FStaying dry and warm through the day.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
