OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FVariable
OL,6,Fcloud and sunny spells for Glasgow on
OL,7,FSunday and staying mainly dry, Cloudy
OL,8,Fwith patchy rain for a time for
OL,9,FArgyll. Staying dry, warm and sunny
OL,10,FMonday and Tuesday.
